OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1775139066
OL,3,CBuzzard left trapped in car grille
OL,4,Cmakes 'remarkable' recovery
OL,6,FVolunteers at an animal rescue centre
OL,7,Fin Oxfordshire have hailed the
OL,8,F"remarkable transformation" of a
OL,9,Fbuzzard taken into their care after
OL,10,Frescuing it from the grille of a car.
OL,12,FOxfordshire Wildlife Rescue (OWR)
OL,13,Fresponded to a emergency call on March
OL,14,F15, after the bird of prey was hit
OL,15,Fnear Watlington by a 4x4 vehicle,
OL,16,Fbecoming trapped in its front grille.
OL,18,FAn image taken after responders
OL,19,Farrived at the scene shows the buzzard
OL,20,Fspread across the front of the car,
OL,21,Fclose to its left headlight.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
