OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1775139066
OL,3,CBuzzard left trapped in car grille
OL,4,Cmakes 'remarkable' recovery
OL,6,FBut, despite the apparent severity of
OL,7,Fthe incident, the female bird suffered
OL,8,Fonly a torn wing and a serious
OL,9,Fheadache, with vets carefully removing
OL,10,Fit without causing further distress.
OL,12,FOWR said in a social media post that
OL,13,Fthe caller had done "exactly the right
OL,14,Fthing" in reporting the incident
OL,15,Fimmediately and not attempting to free
OL,16,Fthe bird themselves.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
