FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1775139066
OL,3,CBuzzard left trapped in car grille
OL,4,Cmakes 'remarkable' recovery
OL,6,F"The reason for this is that buzzards
OL,7,Fhave a formidable pair of talons and
OL,8,Fbeing 'footed' or grabbed by them can
OL,9,Fbe a very painful experience," the
OL,10,Forganisation said.
OL,12,FAn update on the bird's health, which
OL,13,Fwas shared towards the end of March,
OL,14,Frevealed that, after a period of care,
OL,15,Fit had made an "incredible" change in
OL,16,Fits physical health.
OL,18,FIt also shared several pictures of the
OL,19,Fbuzzard looking a picture of health,
OL,20,Fwith its wing fully healed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
